name: lesshat
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "lesshat" %}
{% set version = "4.1.0" %}
{% set sha256 = "4392d15f445d9a1b6b38d47f6317dc29ddcba81a813ede620dd6d9221b26abe6" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://github.com/madebysource/{{ name }}/archive/{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: {{ sha256 }}

build:
  number: 0
  noarch: generic
  script: |
    tgz=$(npm pack)
    npm install -g $tgz

requirements:
  build:
    - nodejs
  
test:
  commands:
    - npm list -g lesshat
  requires:
    - nodejs
   

about:
  home: https://github.com/madebysource/lesshat
  license: MIT
  license_family: MIT
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: 'Smart LESS CSS mixins library.'
  description: |
    Smart LESS CSS mixins library.
  doc_url: https://github.com/madebysource/lesshat#documentation
  dev_url: https://github.com/madebysource/lesshat

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - cshaley
    - sannykr
